'From Squeak3.1alpha of 4 February 2001 [latest update: #3704] on 23 February 2001 at 4:46:04 pm'!"Change Set:		InvisibleGrab-arDate:			23 February 2001Author:			Andreas RaabFixes the attempt to grab an invisible morph."!!PasteUpMorph methodsFor: 'event handling' stamp: 'ar 2/23/2001 16:44'!morphToGrab: event	"Return the morph to grab from a mouse down event. If none, return nil."	self submorphsDo:[:m|		((m rejectsEvent: event) not and:[m fullContainsPoint: event cursorPoint]) ifTrue:[^m].	].	^nil! !